<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Chatrat" description="Privacy policy for Chatrat VSCode extension">
	<!-- Navigation -->
	<nav class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
			<div class="flex justify-between items-center py-4">
				<div class="nav-brand">
					<a href="/" class="no-underline"><h2 class="text-pink-500 text-2xl font-bold tracking-widest">üí¨üêÄ<span class="tracking-normal">.</span>üòπ</h2></a>
				</div>
				<div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 items-center">
					<a href="/" class="font-medium text-gray-800 hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors duration-200">Home</a>
					<a href="/#features" class="font-medium text-gray-800 hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors duration-200">Features</a>
					<a href="/#how-it-works" class="font-medium text-gray-800 hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors duration-200">How it Works</a>
					<a href="/terms" class="font-medium text-gray-800 hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors duration-200">Terms</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
	<main class="py-16 bg-yellow-50 min-h-screen">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
			<div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 rounded-xl shadow-md">
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
				<p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 italic">Last updated: August 2025</p>

				<section class="mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-pink-500">1. Information We Collect</h2>
					<p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Chatrat is designed with privacy as a core principle. We collect minimal information necessary to provide our service:</p>
					<ul class="mb-4 pl-6 space-y-2">
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800"><strong>Local Code Analysis:</strong> The extension analyzes your codebase locally on your machine to create an index</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800"><strong>Usage Analytics:</strong> Basic, anonymized usage statistics to improve the extension (optional and can be disabled)</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800"><strong>Error Reports:</strong> Crash reports and error logs to help us fix bugs (no code content included)</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-pink-500">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
					<p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Your code and project information is processed entirely on your local machine:</p>
					<ul class="mb-4 pl-6 space-y-2">
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Code indexing happens locally within VSCode</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">File content is shared only through the MCP protocol when you explicitly reference files</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">No code is uploaded to our servers or third-party services</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Analytics data is used solely to improve the extension's performance and features</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-pink-500">3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
					<ul class="mb-4 pl-6 space-y-2">
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800"><strong>Local Storage:</strong> All code indexes and metadata are stored locally on your machine</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800"><strong>No Cloud Storage:</strong> We do not store your code or project data on any remote servers</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800"><strong>Secure Communication:</strong> MCP protocol communications are handled securely within your local environment</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800"><strong>Data Encryption:</strong> Local data is encrypted using industry-standard methods</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-pink-500">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
					<p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Chatrat may interact with:</p>
					<ul class="mb-4 pl-6 space-y-2">
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800"><strong>VSCode Marketplace:</strong> For extension updates and installation</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800"><strong>LLM Providers:</strong> When you choose to connect the MCP server to AI services (data sharing controlled by you)</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800"><strong>Analytics Services:</strong> For anonymized usage statistics (can be opted out)</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-pink-500">5. Your Rights and Controls</h2>
					<p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-800">You have full control over your data:</p>
					<ul class="mb-4 pl-6 space-y-2">
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Disable analytics collection in extension settings</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Delete local indexes at any time</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Control which files are indexed through .gitignore-style configuration</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Disconnect from MCP server at any time</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-pink-500">6. Data Retention</h2>
					<ul class="mb-4 pl-6 space-y-2">
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Local indexes are retained until you uninstall the extension or manually delete them</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Analytics data is retained for 12 months maximum</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Error logs are retained for 6 months for debugging purposes</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-pink-500">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Our service is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
				</section>

				<section class="mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-pink-500">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes through the extension or our website.</p>
				</section>

				<section class="mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-pink-500">9. Contact Us</h2>
					<p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-800">If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at:</p>
					<ul class="mb-4 pl-6 space-y-2">
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">Email: grep@chatrat.cat</li>
						<li class="leading-relaxed text-gray-800">GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/alexjamesgodfrey/chatrat" class="text-pink-500 underline hover:text-pink-600">github.com/alexjamesgodfrey/chatrat</a></li>
					</ul>
				</section>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>

	<!-- Footer -->
	<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-12">
		<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-8">
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-pink-500 text-xl font-bold mb-2">Chatrat</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-300">Smart codebase context for LLM conversations</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Product</h4>
					<div class="space-y-2">
						<a href="/#features" class="block text-gray-300 hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors duration-200">Features</a>
						<a href="/#how-it-works" class="block text-gray-300 hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors duration-200">How it Works</a>
						<a href="https://github.com/alexjamesgodfrey/chatrat" class="block text-gray-300 hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors duration-200">GitHub</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Legal</h4>
					<div class="space-y-2">
						<a href="/privacy" class="block text-gray-300 hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors duration-200">Privacy Policy</a>
						<a href="/terms" class="block text-gray-300 hover:text-pink-500 transition-colors duration-200">Terms of Service</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="border-t border-gray-800 pt-4 text-center">
				<p class="text-gray-300">&copy; 2025 Chatrat. Contact us at <a href="mailto:grep@chatrat.cat" class="text-pink-500 hover:text-pink-400 transition-colors duration-200">grep@chatrat.cat</a></p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</footer>
</Layout>


